snippet.title: Secret Kingdom Defenders - Update Trailer!
snippet.description:
Play on iOS: https://goo.gl/h3TG7g
Play on Google Play: https://goo.gl/ZkKM4w

A young monk is making a fateful journey westward, but he can't do it alone! Along the way, he'll encounter bull demons, friendly pigs, flying dragon knights, and greatest of all, a mischievous Monkey King determined to test the monk's strength of will...
